itemLabel: Ralph Harris, Baron Harris of High Cross

wikipedia_page.main: Ralph Harris, Baron Harris of High Cross (10 December 1924 – 19 October 2006) was a British economist. He was head of the Institute of Economic Affairs from 1957 to 1988.
